  - m_Id: 356990020462305280
    m_Localized: 'Briefing: Displays the message at the start of the mission<br>Debriefing
      (Victory): Displays the message at the end of the mission in the event of a
      victory<br>Debriefing (Defeat): Displays the message at the end of the mission
      in the event of a defeat'
